title: Top Places to visit in Maharajganj, Uttar Pradesh
content: Mahrajganj is a town and a municipal board in Maharajganj district in the Indian state of Uttar Pradesh.Maharajganj District of Uttar Pradesh achieved autonomy on 2 October 1989. This rectangular district spans from 27°09' North to 83°34' East geometric coordinates and occupies 2934.1 km2
